# RZGB Project — Cursor Rules

## Stack
- Frontend: HTML/CSS/JS (Bootstrapmade template)
- Backend: Node.js on Hostinger
- Database: Supabase
- Deploy: GitHub push → Hostinger auto-deploy

## Project URLs
- Main site: rzglobalsolutions.co.uk
- Portal: portal.rzglobalsolutions.co.uk

## User Roles
- Client: submits orders, tracks progress
- RZ Global (admin): manages full workflow
- Supplier: receives jobs, updates stage progress

## Order Workflow Stages
Quote → Casting/Forging → Machining → QC → Packaging → Delivery

## Code Style
- Vanilla JS preferred unless otherwise specified
- Keep HTML/CSS/JS in separate files
- Use Supabase client for all DB calls
- No frameworks unless already in use

